title: #AskGaryVee Audiobook: Chapter 17 Self-Awareness
description:
This is a chapter from the #AskGaryVee audiobook, Chapter 17: Self-Awareness.  If you haven't checked out the audiobook yet, it's one of the best and most important chapters I recorded and wanted to make sure all of you had a chance to listen to it. 

The #AskGaryVee audiobook showcases the most useful and interesting questions I've addressed on the show, distilling and expanding on this podcast's most urgent and evergreen themes. For more info on the book or the audiobook you can check out http://bit.ly/AGVaudiobook. 

Thanks for listening!
